# Why
I want to centralized all the informations that I have gathered using CMake and Travis-CI.

# What
## Done

1. CMake
   - Catch2 unittest
   - Debug and Release configuration
   - Make and Ninja build system

2. Travis-CI
   - Email notification
   - Check whitespace trailing
   - GNU g++-5/6/7
   - Clang 4.0, 5.0
   - Unitttest execution
   - CppCheck

3. Tools
   - travis-ci.com

